flowchart TD
    Inicio --> Try[try: executa operacao]
    Try -->|Sucesso| Finally[finally: executa SEMPRE]
    Try -->|Erro| Catch[catch: captura e trata erro]
    Catch --> Finally
    Finally --> Continue[Continua apos try catch finally]
    Try -->|return dentro do try| FinallyBeforeReturn[finally executa ANTES do return]
    FinallyBeforeReturn --> Return[return efetivado]

    style Try fill:#90EE90,stroke:#333
    style Catch fill:#FFB6C1,stroke:#333
    style Finally fill:#ADD8E6,stroke:#333
    style FinallyBeforeReturn fill:#ADD8E6,stroke:#333